Hi there!

I am Mr. DAPs, that guy with the hat that walks around Disneyland. I will mainly be posting some pictures that I have taken that I particularly like here but will occasionally post some other things.

You can read some of my other posts at any or all of the links below:

Blog: mrdaps.com
Website: dapsmagic.com
Twitter: twitter.com/mrdaps
Facebook: facebook.com/misterdaps

Please feel free to add me on any or all of the above links. I look forward to chatting with you and seeing you in the park!

Make it a GREAT day!

-Mr. DAPs

summary: Disneyland Resort to Welcome Captain Marvel Early Next Year
title: Disneyland Resort to Welcome Captain Marvel Early Next Year
body:
Disneyland Resort to Welcome Captain Marvel Early Next Year

The Disneyland Resort will be welcoming Captain Marvel early in 2019. Captain Marvel will be arriving in theaters on March 8, 2019, and will be stopping by Disney California Adventure for a limited time to meet with guests.

Captain Marvel will be joining the other incredible Marvel heroes at Disney California Adventure. This includes Captain America, Spider-Man, Black Panther and the Dora Milaje.

summary: Captain Marvel coming to Disney California Adventure in early 2019
title: Captain Marvel coming to Disney California Adventure in early 2019
body:
Disney announced today that Captain Marvel will be coming to Disney California Adventure in early 2019.

It has already been announced that she will also be joining the Marvel Day at Sea aboard the Disney Cruise Line and will also be added to the Marvel Summer of Super Heroes in 2019.

Captain Marvel will join Black Panther and the Dora Milaje, Spider-Man and Captain America.

Captain Marvel hits theaters on March 8, 2019.

Be sure to follow us on Twitter and Facebook for the latest news, photos and more from Disneyland Resort!

Captain Marvel coming to Disney California Adventure in early 2019 was originally published on
